Hey, are you heading home?

4
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:51,009
Yes, sir. See you tomorrow.

5
00:00:51,092 --> 00:00:53,595
Hey, take this with you.

6
00:00:53,678 --> 00:00:54,846
