What the hell is this?

69
00:06:46,447 --> 00:06:48,282
I fell asleep on the couch.

70
00:06:50,451 --> 00:06:52,370
You're not going to bed? It's late.

71
00:06:52,453 --> 00:06:53,704
Go ahead.

72
00:06:54,997 --> 00:06:56,582
All right. I'm going to sleep.

73
00:06:59,335 --> 00:07:02,130
Turn on the lights when you watch TV.
It's bad for your eyes.

74
00:07:45,882 --> 00:07:47,300
Who is that woman?

75
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:11,699
Geez!

76
00:08:25,671 --> 00:08:27,381
Honey, get inside!

77
00:10:00,474 --> 00:10:02,143
5 MINUTES A DAY, MOTHER'S VOICE

78
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:40,931
Yes, Captain.

79
00:10:42,433 --> 00:10:44,518
Go ahead. I was already awake.

80
00:10:45,561 --> 00:10:46,604
What?

81
00:10:47,813 --> 00:10:49,190
What do you mean?

82
00:10:52,568 --> 00:10:53,736
Hold on a minute.

83
