00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:32,520
Sir.

112
00:13:33,187 --> 00:13:34,522
You have a guest.

113
00:13:38,317 --> 00:13:39,401
Oh my.

114
00:13:39,485 --> 00:13:42,238
Did you have any trouble
finding my office?

115
00:13:45,950 --> 00:13:48,494
We took that photo
during your farewell ceremony.

116
00:13:48,577 --> 00:13:50,120
You don't remember it, do you?

117
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:55,668
All the staff members cried that day.

118
00:13:56,335 --> 00:13:57,670
